### Security.
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
  Header always set Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'https' 'self';"
  Header always set Content-Security-Policy "frame-src platform.twitter.com;"
  Header always set Content-Security-Policy "img-src 'self' data: i.ytimg.com www.google-analytics.com;"
  Header always set Content-Security-Policy "object-src 'https' 'self';"
  Header always set Content-Security-Policy "script-src 'self' www.google-analytics.com ajax.googleapis.com platform.twitter.com;"

  Header always set Strict-Transport-Security "max-age=15768000;"
  Header always set X-Content-Type-Options nosniff
  Header always append X-Frame-Options "SAMEORIGIN"
  Header always set X-XSS-Protection "1; mode=block"

  Header always append Vary Accept-Encoding
</IfModule>

### Protect against DOS attacks by limiting file upload size
LimitRequestBody 10240000

### Deny directory listing.
Options -Indexes

# <Directory "/scratch">
#   Deny from all
# </Directory>

### Etag for multiple servers better FileETag None.
FileETag MTime Size

### Add correct content-type for documents, fonts and images.
<IfModule mod_mime.c>
  AddType application/pdf .pdf
  AddType application/vnd.ms-fontobject .eot

  AddType font/otf .otf
  AddType font/ttf .ttf
  AddType font/x-woff .woff

  AddType image/gif .gif
  AddType image/jpeg .jpg .jpeg .jpe
  AddType image/png .png
  AddType image/svg+xml .svg

  ### Compression.
  AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE application/json application/x-javascript font/otf font/ttf image/svg+xml text/css text/html text/plain text/xml
</IfModule>

